{"tid":259481,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼城4300萬鎊簽摩納哥貝拿度施華","createTime":"2017-05-27T03:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T09:21:04.000Z","uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f4f194a64dd5b25385aab222e5145fb6ea259190","tid":259481,"uid":10199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"曼城閃電展開大換血行動，宣佈以4300萬英鎊簽入摩納哥23歲中場貝拿度施華，成為今夏第一名新兵。<br />\n<br />\n薩巴列達加盟韋斯咸<br />\n<br />\n在宣佈捷西斯拿華斯、基捷基治等4人將會離隊後不足24小時，曼城即完成第一宗收購行動，貝拿度施華今季協助摩納哥在法甲封王及打入歐聯4強，表現有目共睹。他在周五已向曼城報到並完成體測，正式簽下5年合約。<br />\n<br />\n這位葡萄牙中場指揮官坦言，哥迪奧拿是他決定加盟「藍月亮」的主要原因︰「即使他未必是世上最佳領隊，也一定是其中一位，他在巴塞及拜仁捧盃無數，能夠與他合作實在太好。我很高興可加盟曼城，它是現今其中一支最佳球隊，我希望可協助他們達成目標。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=zfRtdHnOVVvzwxkSvS6ahP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=fd163749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"61cfca7fd2f0dd6362351ad94e95090eca16a3c9","tid":259481,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:19:41.000Z","msg":"psg又可以坐定粒六捧法甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac44800d33eeeda010ec971337fe2ee780887249","tid":259481,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:32:58.000Z","msg":"會清邊4人？"},{"pid":"4835ff2c2ffee2921c6a4b6f2e3f57530dd6835a","tid":259481,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T06:11:15.000Z","msg":"咁快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44b8cfbb0de9bc0612cfca79f13fce088b53348","tid":259481,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T06:24:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會清邊4人？</blockquote><br />\n左閘基治<br />\n右閘薩巴sagna 拿左角大<br />\n門將 卡巴尼路<br />\n中堅文加拉<br />\n全部已清走"},{"pid":"a3c3ea38280b7169536fb97140050866defaeb06","tid":25948